com.amazonaws.services.dynamodbv2.datamodeling

Annotation Type DynamoDBTypeConvertedEpochDate


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={FIELD,METHOD})
public @interface DynamoDBTypeConvertedEpochDate
    Annotation to convert a date object (Date, Calendar, DateTime) to a ScalarAttributeType.N stored as epoch time.

    Alternately, the DynamoDBTyped annotation may be used,

     @DynamoDBTyped(DynamoDBAttributeType.N)
 public Date getDate()
    See Also:
    DynamoDBTypeConverted
